::KitKat::

She was about to start working on the clone again when the alarm went 
off.  She walked to the monitor and silenced the alarm.  She checked 
the outside scanners. "Starscream, we seem to have somebot spying on 
us.  ANd it appears to be maximal. Would my War General be so kind 
and fetch this bot for me.  I want to find out why he is here and 
what he knows before he meets the matrix."  she smiled at the 
thought. She needed a way to vent her frustrations and taking it out 
on a maximal was the perfect way to do it.
